d about how they handle the quests (yay, quest books!) and am really looking forward to seeing how their skill system works. <br><br>Keep in mind that I haven't actually played the game yet, not being in the Beta (and I don't think I'm saying anything that hasn't already been said in public forums).  It looks, though, from what I've seen that Mythic is doing a great job of developing a stable game system to house their content and that the RvR (realm vs realm, a type of pvp) stuff at the high level game will come into play just when you really start hitting the point of 'if I have to camp another damn drolvarg, I think I'll kill myself'.  Replace drolvarg with whatever monster people are killing for xp at those levels in DAoC. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Overall, it just looks very interesting and I'm eager to see how the lessons they learned from watching and playing EQ translate into the game that Mythic produces.<br><br>I'll stop evangalizing now. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>p.s. tried to spell check, but can't connect to the spell check server. bah. <p><center><img src=http://www.idiom.com/~mony/gifs/kyenasig3.jpg><br>Bard of the 49th Song<br>Ancient Prophecy<br>Mithaniel Marr</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#DEEFDE><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub18.ezboard.com/usaraine.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saraine</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.gulftel.com/saraine/images/fire1.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of Polls<br>MMDN Opinion Editor<br><img src=http:/